        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><hr /><p>Beyond emulating dragonkin's energy breath, you've now learned to channel the power of a true dragon, able to spew forth its potent energy. Choose a type of damage that corresponds to a specific dragon. You can exhale this energy as a @Template[cone|distance:15] or @Template[line|distance:30] that deals @Damage[14d6[untyped],4d6[persistent,untyped]|options:area-damage]{14d6 damage plus 4d6 persistent} damage of the chosen type (basic @Check[reflex|against:class-spell|basic|options:area-effect,inflicts:frightened] save using the higher of your class DC or spell DC). On a critical failure, a target also becomes @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>"
        },
